Name: FirstPlanet
About the game: First Planet is a 2.5D barrage shooting game that uses energy to develop planets and defeat enemies of the universe. prologue : You were chosen to be the commander of a planet. Shoot, avoid, develop, and clear every chapter to find out the secrets of the beautiful universe.
